::{{DIcon}} I was hoping we could talk...
:::'''Danae:''' Sure. What would you like to discuss?
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504053003_46-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504053003_46-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Could you share more about your mother?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504053113-->
::::'''Danae:''' The story of how the Holy Maiden saved my mother... I've heard it countless times, but it still warms my heart every time I hear it.
::::'''Danae:''' She was very young. It was a bitterly cold, snowy day, and she didn't even have a single crumb to eat at home. She lingered outside the temple for a long time before discovering a tiny hole at the base of the wall. Overwhelmed by hunger, she crawled through...
::::'''Danae:''' She intended to steal some offerings at the statue's feet but was caught by a priest. My mom told me she trembled with fear, convinced her fate was sealed. However, when the priest took her to the interrogation room, by chance, the Holy Maiden was also present.
::::'''Danae:''' The Holy Maiden spoke gently. "How long have you been without food? You are thin as a stick?" After offering my mother some of her snacks and ensuring my mother had enough strength, she packed a large bag of treats for my mother to take home.
::::'''Danae:''' The Holy Maiden also urged her to take care of herself. Over the years, my mother has always wanted to repay the kindness, but meeting the Holy Maiden isn't something we can simply do. Instead, she instilled that deep gratitude in us.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} What do you usually do here each day?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504053119-->
::::'''Danae:''' When I have some spare time, I pitch in with tidying up around here &mdash; pulling weeds, scraping moss off the walls, and the like.
::::'''Danae:''' Besides that &mdash; as you probably know &mdash; I help visitors find their way around, acting as a volunteer guide.
::::'''Danae:''' Given the complexity of the paths here, and with many areas being off-limits, it's easy for newcomers to get lost, which could lead to trouble.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Have you met any interesting people here?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504053123-->
::::'''Danae:''' Well, not necessarily interesting, as everyone who comes here has their own story to tell.
::::'''Danae:''' The temple attracts devout pilgrims, scholars studying history, and merchants looking to glimpse their future fortunes.
::::'''Danae:''' I find the priests who serve the Titans and the Holy Maiden the most intriguing of all... It makes me curious how they view us mere regular followers.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Exit}} Let's stop here for now. Goodbye.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504053127-->
::::'''Danae:''' Alright, take care. If you run into trouble and need help, remember to look me up.
::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
::{{DIcon|Exit}} It's nothing. I was just passing through.
:::'''Danae:''' Oh, let's catch up in the future. If you run into trouble and need help, remember to look me up.
